2003-05-26 18:40 UTC-0800 Brian Hays <bhays@abacuslaw.com>
  * contrib/rdd_ads/ads1.c
     * fixed logic for GoTo, to remove redundant code and numeric constants

     * Modified adsDeleted for speed and code standards.
       Recent fix to adsDeleted confused the RDD return value of SUCCESS
       and the Advantage-specific return value of AE_SUCCESS, which we
       cannot presume are the same--and certainly the error return
       codes are totally different.

