2003-05-25 17:17 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron@ronpinkas.com>
  * source/pp/ppcore.c
    * Added missing () as per GCC warning.

  * include/hbvmpub.h
    + Added memebr PHB_BASEARRAY pSelfBase to HB_CODEBLOCK structure.

  * source/vm/hvm.c
    + Added logic to reset pModuleSymbols of HB_VM_STACK on termination of hb_vmDo().
    + Added logic to reset pModuleSymbols of HB_VM_STACK on termination of hb_vmExecute().
    + Added logic to store appropriate HB_QSelf() value in each Codeblock. This Greatly improves the utility of HB_QSelf().
    + Added new:

        HB_SaveBlock( <Block> ) -> PersistedBlock Stream

      which can correctly persist any Codeblock.

    + Added new:

        HB_RestoreBlock( <PersistedBlock> ) -> Block

      which can correctly restore any persisted Codeblock. Block must be restored within an Application containing
      the Compiled Module which the original Block was created at.

  + tests/savebloc.prg
    + Added sample test of new HB_Saveblock() and HB_RestoreBlock().

  * source/rtl/cstr.prg
    + Added Block support in ValToPrg() and ValToPrgExp() using new HB_SaveBlcok() and HB_RestoreBlock()

  * source/rtl/persist.prg
    + Added Block support using new HB_SaveBlcok() and HB_RestoreBlock()

  * source/vm/classes.c
    + Added logic to hb_clsValidScope() to take advantage of Codeblock embeded HB_QSelf() value. This solved 2 newly discovered scope bugs.

  * source/vm/estack.c
    + Added logic to initilize pSymbolModule member of HB_STACK in hb_stackInit().

  * source/compiler/harbour.sly
    + Added Line Number generation to MEMEBER_DECLARE Statements. This solved missing line numbers for Blocks created at Class Functions.

  * include/hbcomp.h
  * source/compiler/gencobj.c
  * source/compiler/genc.c
    + Added 3rd param char * szSourcePath to hb_compGenCCode() and hb_compGenCObj()

  * source/compiler/harbour.c
    * Added 3rd paramater char *szSourcePath to hb_compGenOutput()
    + Added logic to retain source file path, and pass it as 3rd paramater to hb_compGenOutput()
      which then forwards it to hb_compGenCCode() and hb_compGenCObj()

  * source/compiler/genc.c
    + Added logic to convert '\' to '/' in __PRG_SOURCE__ to correct display problem.
    + Added logic to use source file path when generating __PRG_SOURCE__

  * source/vm/extend.c
    + Added HB_IT_DATE and HB_IT_STRING support in hb_param() when Mask is HB_IT_NUMERIC.

  * source/vm/itemapi.c
    + Added HB_IT_DATE and HB_IT_STRING support in hb_itemNLen()
    + Added HB_IT_DATE and HB_IT_STRING support in hb_itemStr()

  * tests/tstscope.prg
    + Added test of a Data Block using INIT accessing restriced scope Data.

  * tests/testpers.prg
    + Added Block proerty to demonstrate HBPersist support for Block type.

