2003-05-22 20:23 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron@ronpinkas.com>
  * source/vm/arrays.c
  * include/hbapi.h
    + Added new hb_arraySetForward( PHB_ITEM pArray, ULONG ulIndex, PHB_ITEM pItem ); /* sets an array element by forwarding it's value */

  * source/vm/classes.c
    - Removed redunandant function HB_FUNC( __CLASSSELPERSISTENT ) /* see HB_FUNC( __CLSGETPROPERTIES ) */
    + Added new HB_FUNC( __CLSGETPROPERTIESANDVALUES ) returning Array of Sub-Arrays of { cProperty, xValue }

  * source/rtl/cstr.prg
    + Added new ValtoPrgExp( xValue ) returning a valid source string representing the value of any type.
    * Improved ValToPrg() to support Block type.

  * source/rtl/persist.prg
    * Rewrote LoadFromText() and SaveToText() from scratch.
    % Greatly optimized SaveToText() by utilizing new __clsGetPropertiesAndValues() which is far faster then sending messages to the Object.
    ! Completed LoadFromText() to support nested Objects.

  * source/rtl/hbserial.prg
    % Greatly optimized HB_Serilaize() by utilizing new __clsGetPropertiesAndValues() which is far faster then sending messages to the Object.

  * tests/testpers.prg
    * Extended sample to show new ability to restore Nested objects from stream.

  * source/vm/hvm.c
    ! Fixed hb_vmEqual() to correctly handle comparison of empty arrays.

