    ! Parameters 3 and 4 of AT() were not sanitized nor checked,
      causing endless loops/segfaults on misbehaving programs.
      Currently, they have been sanitized, but probably the
      correct thing to do there is to issue an out of bound
      error.

2003-05-17 17:30 UTC+0200 Przemyslaw Czerpak <druzus@polbox.com>
  * xharbour/bin/hb-mkslib.sh
  * xharbour/make_rpm.sh
  * xharbour/xharbour.spec
  * xharbour/source/rtl/gtcrs/gtcrs.h
