2003-05-17 04:22 UTC+0200 Przemyslaw Czerpak <druzus@polbox.com>
  * xharbour/bin/!pack_src.sh
    * some minor modifications

  + xharbour/bin/hb-mkslib.sh
    + simple script to build shared libraries from static ones and object
      files

  + xharbour/xharbour.spec
    + RPM spec to build xHarbour binaries RPMs. It produce three RPMs
      xharbour (compiler and tools), xharbour-lib (shared xHarbour libraries
      for developers and users of application linked with shard libs)
      xharbour-static (static libs for developers who want to produce static
      binaries). xharbour rpm has additional tools 'xhbcmp', 'xhlnk', 'xhbmk'
      See README.RPM for detailed description.

  + xharbour/make_rpm.sh
    + simple script which automaticaly packs the CVS tree and builds
      RPMs

