    * changes to compile on OS/2 with EMX GCC compiler

  NOTE: With these changes the single threaded xHarbour can be built on OS/2 using EMX GCC
        If a compiled program wants to use xHarbour socket support it has to be linked
        with -lsocket to add socket library to resulting .exe file

