2003-04-21 00:44 UTC+0100 Giancarlo Niccolai <gian@niccolai.ws>
  * include/hbapi.h
  * source/vm/hvm.c
    + Added the C function hb_execFromArray( PHB_ITEM caItem ), which is
      similar to the PRG HB_ExecFromArray, except for the fact that
      accepts only a "callable" array:
      caItem = { @Func(),...} or { "FuncName",...}
      caItem = { oObject, nMethodPtr,...} or { oObject, "MethodName",...}

  * include/inet.h
  * source/vm/inet.c
    ! Fixed some imprecisions in stack locking for MT
    + Added the Timelimit and Periodc callback system.
      InetSetTimelimit( Socket, nTimelimit ) -->NIL
      InetGetTimelimit( Socket ) --> nTimelimit
      InetClearTimelimit( Socket ) --> Nil

      InetSetPeriodicCallback( Socket, caPeriodicCallback ) --> NIL
      InetGetPeriodicCallback( Socket ) --> caPeriodicCallback or NIL
      InetClearPeriodicCallback( Socket ) --> NIL

  * tests/server.prg
    + Added test for a periodic callback

  * source/rtl/trpccli.prg
    + Added some accessors to screen local variables.

  * source/rtl/hbsrlraw.c
    + Added suport for objects containing NIL properties.

