2003-04-13 01:27 UTC+0100 Giancarlo Niccolai <gian@niccolai.ws>
  * source/rtl/hbreadini.prg
    ! Due to a mistyping, separator character to have more than one
      possible ini to be searched (in the parameter) was ":".
      In Italian keyboard ";" and ":" are one at the side of
      the other... :-(
      The correct character is ";", althoug ":" is used storically
      as a path separator in UNIX, ";" is used in all the cross
      platform languages (inlcuding PHP, Python and Perl).

