2003-03-27 21:50 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron@ronpinkas.com>
  * include/hbexprb.c
  * source/compiler/harbour.sly
    * Improved support for Instance Var BY-REF to not require the "()".
    * Improved support for MacroExp BY-REF, to support any valid macro expression.

  /*
     NOTE: New Syntax is simply:

        @<AnyExp>:<Indentifier>
        @&<SomeMacro>
        @&<SomeMacro.Suffix>
        @&( <AnyExp> )

     Such reference may be passed as argument to a Function Call, or may be embeded in a Literal Array.
   */

  * tests/ivarref.prg
  * tests/macroref.prg
    * Enhanced testing and demo.

