2003-03-27 13:56 UTC+0100 Giancarlo Niccolai <gian@niccolai.ws>
  * source/rtl/hbreadini.prg
    + Added function HB_SetIniComment( cLc, cHlc ) --> NIL, where cLc is
      the "Line comment", valid only if it is the first non blank
      character on a line, and cHlc is the "half line comment", vaild
      wherever it's found (thus in the middle of a line).
      Defaults are ";" for the line comment and "#" for the half line
      comment; call HB_SetIniComment( "", ";" ) to have Microsoft like
      ini comment style.

