  * source/rtl/hbreadini.prg
    + Added HB_WriteIni( cFile, aaIni [, cBeginComment [, cEndComment]])
            --> lResult
      If cFile is a string the file is created, while if it is a number
      (a file handler) an already open file is used. This is useful
      for writing by-hand some part of the config file and then pass
      the resto to HB_WriteIni()

  * tests/parseini.ini
  * tests/parseini.prg
    + Added test for HB_WriteIni()

