2003-03-03 10:40 UTC-0300 Luiz Rafael Culik <culikr@uol.com.br>
  * makefile.bc
    ! Standarize CFLAGS to -5 -6 -OS -a8 -DHB_FM_STATISTICS_OFF
      and ARFLAGS to /0 (reduce lib size in about 10-20%)

