2003-02-28 02:30 UTC-0800 Ron Pinkas <ron@ronpinkas.com>
  * include/hbexpra.c
  * include/hbexprb.c
  * include/hbexprop.h
  * include/hbpcode.h
  * source/common/expropt1.c
  * source/compiler/genc.c
  * source/compiler/hbpcode.c
  * source/compiler/harbour.slx
  * source/compiler/harbour.sly
  * source/compiler/hbfix.c
  * source/vm/hvm.c
    + Added support for new operators HAS and LIKE.

    /*
      Syntax: cExp HAS  cRegEx|CompiledRegEx => bMatch
              cExp LIKE cRegEx|CompiledRegEx => bLike

      HAS will return .T. if cExp contains a match to the specified Regular Expression.
      LIKE will return .T. if all of its text is a match to the specified Regular Expression.
    */

  * source/rtl/regex.c
    + Added low level worker function hb_regex().
    - Removed work logic from HB_REGEX() and HB_REGEXMATCH() and modified them as wrappers to hb_regex().
    % Few optimizations.

  * xdiff.txt
    * Updated with new operators HAS and LIKE.

  + tests/has_like.prg
    + Added small test of new HAS and LIKE operators.

2003-02-28 06:55 UTC-0300 Marcelo Lombardo <lombardo@uol.com.br>
