   NOTE: This is a work in progress, and exactly a BEGIN of a LONG work.
   I have made sure that this commit works with mttest.prg and mtgc.prg,
   and I commit it because I need to show this changes to other developers
   involved in the project, and to port the source to my windows test
   machines. Other programs, (involving classes, RDD and array management)
   are NOT going to work with this commit, because the develpement of the
   new framework has just started.

